				<div style="font-style:italic">So - you're advocating vigilante justice, then?  Publicize her whereabouts and let someone on the outside kill her?  <br />
<br />
Or perhaps advocating an abuse of the &quot;mental disorder&quot; standard to institutionalize her?  She's not crazy - she's evil.  Evil is not a mental disorder.<br />
